name: 2-Box Pivot Window
description:
Explore our wooden frame, consisting of two compartments. On the right is a suspended wooden pivot window. Whereas the left includes a fixed glass compartment. Despite the different uses, both windows are made with the same wood for a seamless look. All pivot windows open outwards and are perfect for upper floors. You can also explore our tilt-and-turn windows if you’re looking for an inward turning window.

Customize your profile

You can choose your own profile of the wooden frames. Browse our website to explore the possibilities, including pre-painted or top coated frames.

All our frames are made to measure. Simply include your dimensions and order the frame. Customize your fit and coating with some of our many choices. We include glass ratings from HR++ glass to triple glass. Regardless of your choice, all our frames are glazed from the inside, which leads to a more modern and sleek appearance all while being more effective in burglar resistance.

Explore our offerings to customize your own window set up today.

name: 2-Compartment TIlt and Turn Window (left) with Fixed Glass
description:
Discover this sturdy and meticulously-crafted wooden frame, featuring two equal compartments. The left includes a tilt-and-turn window with a right compartment with fixed glass, which always opens inwards.

This high-quality wooden frame includes a completely assembled hung tilt-and-turn window, including fittings. All fitting complies with the SKG quality mark and the Policy Quality Mark for Safe Living.

Customize your setup! The wooden tilt-and-turn windows can be assembled in various arrangements.

Options for glazing

We offer several options for glazing to your preferences. Choose from standard HR++ glass, 2-sided laminated HR++ glass to triple glass. Explore our options and choose the glazing that suits your preferences. Feel peace of mind and safety with interior side glazing, enhancing burglary resistance and superior optical appearance for the frame.

name: 1-Box Turn-tilt Wood Window
description:
Discover our tilt and turn window. This setup includes one compartment complete with a wooden tilt-and-turn window that opens inwards and tilts, perfect for wafting in some fresh air.

This high-quality wooden frame includes a completely assembled hung tilt-and-turn window, including fittings. All fitting complies with the SKG quality mark and the Policy Quality Mark for Safe Living.

Customize your set up! The wooden tilt-and-turn windows can be assembled in various arrangements.

Options for glazing

We offer several options for glazing to your preferences. Choose from standard HR++ glass, 2-sided laminated HR++ glass to triple glass. Explore our options and choose the glazing that suits your preferences. Feel peace of mind and safety with interior side glazing, enhancing burglary resistance and superior optical appearance for the frame.

name: Wooden Fixed Glass Frame | 3 Horizontal Compartments
description:
This 3-compartment wooden fixed glass frame is divided into three horizontally-configured compartments, customized to your preferences. We make all frames to order, giving you the freedom to enter the dimensions and customize the division yourself.

All [insert company name] frames are designed to adhere to the SKG quality mark and the Policy Quality Mark for Safe Living. Customize your frame by choosing a delivery option that includes either a topcoat or prepaint layer.

Options for glazing

Feel peace of mind and safety with interior side glazing, enhancing burglary resistance and superior optical appearance for the frame. We affix an aluminum glazing profile to the sill. Choose from a range of glass choices, including triple glass (HR+++), double glass (HR++), frosted glass, or glass with bars. Or, choose to order the frame without glazing.

Regardless of your customization preferences, the frame is delivered fully assembled. Simply input the dimensions of the wooden frame, the desired properties, and you’re ready to place your order.
